1948;;The Kissing Bandit;;American;;Laslo Benedek;;Frank Sinatra, Kathryn Grayson;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Kissing_Bandit_(film);;The film is set in the early nineteenth century. Ricardo (Frank Sinatra) is the son of a robber known as the Kissing Bandit. He however is a shy, Boston-bred young man who does not know how to sit on a horse. He falls for the daughter of the Spanish Governor of California.